snippet.title: Brute Horse - Official Reveal Trailer | gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
Check out this funny teaser trailer for Brute Horse, an upcoming game from the creators of Ministry of Broadcast. Brute Horse will be available on PlayStation, Xbox, and Steam in 2025.
